    "parsing_res_list": [
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Vision-Language Models, making it suitable for lower end hardware environments [7].\n\n",
            "block_bbox": [
                210,
                166,
                1044,
                232
            ],
            "block_id": 0,
            "block_order": 1
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "The pipeline comprises six core modules: Layout Analysis module identifies 20+hierarchical element classes (titles, tables, formulas, etc.) using PicoDet-L object detection; Text Recognition module employs DBNet for localization and SVTR-LCNet for recognition across 100+ languages; Table Recognition module uses SLANet to predict cell coordinates and HTML tags simultaneously; Formula Recognition module converts mathematical expressions to LaTeX; Chart Understanding module transforms graphs into structured data via PP-Chart2Table;and Reading Order Recovery module ensures logical text flow in multi-column layouts [6].\n\n",
            "block_bbox": [
                210,
                290,
                1044,
                646
            ],
            "block_id": 1,
            "block_order": 2
        },
        {
            "block_label": "paragraph_title",
            "block_content": "#### 2.2. Multi-Format Conversion and Reconstruction ",
            "block_bbox": [
                212,
                703,
                813,
                727
            ],
            "block_id": 2,
            "block_order": 3
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Real world use of OCR software requires it to be compatible with standard formats.While PP-StructureV3 provides native Markdown conversion, this output generates linear content streams that fail to preserve spatial layout [7]. To address complex layout reconstruction limitations of the pipeline, this project implements a custom coordinate-basedreconstruction enginemapping2D coordinatesto absolute-positioned HTML blocks, reconstructing original visual structure.",
            "block_bbox": [
                210,
                791,
                1045,
                1022
            ],
            "block_id": 3,
            "block_order": 4
        },
        {
            "block_label": "paragraph_title",
            "block_content": "#### 2.3. Existing Systems ",
            "block_bbox": [
                211,
                1080,
                465,
                1108
            ],
            "block_id": 4,
            "block_order": 5
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Google Cloud Vision: High multilingual accuracy but requires cloud transmission with elevated costs and lacks local-first privacy [9].",
            "block_bbox": [
                248,
                1150,
                953,
                1216
            ],
            "block_id": 5,
            "block_order": 6
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Adobe Scan: Excellent preprocessing via Adobe AI with integrated assistant,but exhibits reflow errors in multi-column exports and requires cloud processing [10].\n\n",
            "block_bbox": [
                247,
                1258,
                1033,
                1366
            ],
            "block_id": 6,
            "block_order": 7
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Rossum AI: Leader in Intelligent Document Processing for financial documents with natural language querying, optimized for extraction rather than visual reconstruction [11].\n\n",
